cs.IR, cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.DL 

The paper discusses the extraction of data from Web sources using Web wrappers, which is a common topic in Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Database (cs.DB) research. The proposed approach involves creating self-repairing systems, which could fall under the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The paper also mentions the lack of solutions for maintaining these systems, which could be related to Software Engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the use of algorithms and techniques to extract data from Web sources could also be relevant to the Deep Learning (cs.DL) sub-category.
